## Description

Rename agent execution modes from the two-mode `continuous`/`discrete` system to a
clearer three-mode system:

- `:persistent` — Long-running, continuous history, private workspace, compacted context
- `:transient` — Durable memory/files but fresh sessions each run (default)
- `:amnesiac` — No memory, no persistence, cleaned up after job

## Acceptance Criteria

- [x] ExecutionMode module updated with three modes: `:persistent`, `:transient`, `:amnesiac`
- [x] Agent schema updated to use new enum values
- [x] Session schema updated to use new enum values
